    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Limited Amphibiousness. The sahuagin can breathe air and water, but it needs to be submerged at least once every 4 hours to avoid suffocating."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Shark Telepathy. The sahuagin can magically command any shark within 120 feet of it, using a limited telepathy."
    },
